      "writtenOn": "2017-05-18T16:05:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The \u0027tile\u0027 here is treated like an immutable. The mutex is only necessary to swap out the old tile for the new one. The old one will be garbage collected and the new one will be returned by GetTile until a newer once comes around. \nThe same is true for the CacheTile call above. It only reads from the tile.",
